2020-07-27 HENSOLDT Cyber GmbH

    Adapt for the Raspberry Pi 3 Model B+ platform

    * bcm2835.h
        (pragma once): Use `pragma once` instead of include guards.
        (refactoring): Extract GPIO and SPI related features into
                        bcm2837_gpio.h and bcm2837_spio.h and remove unused
                        functionalities.
        (licensing):   Add missing SPDX license id.

    * bcm2835.c
        (refactoring): Extract GPIO and SPI related features into
                        bcm2837_gpio.c and bcm2837_spio.c and remove unused
                        functionalities.
        (licensing):   Add missing SPDX license id.
